GROWTH1=GROWTH_51_data[1:69,]

#converting into time series
GRts=ts(GROWTH1$GROWTH,start = min(GROWTH1$YEAR),end = max(GROWTH1$YEAR),frequency = 1)
# Plot GDP growth
autoplot(GRts) + 
  ylab("GDP Growth Rate (%)") +
  xlab("Year")

# ADF & kpss test

# Fit ARIMA model
arima_model <- auto.arima(GRts, d = 1, max.p = 2, max.q = 1)

# Forecast GDP
arima_forecast <- forecast(arima_model, h = 10)
autoplot(arima_forecast) + 
  ggtitle("ARIMA Forecast for India's GDP Growth") +
  ylab("GDP Growth Rate (%)") +
  xlab("Year")
